========================
Dependencies
========================

- php 5.0
- mysql 5.1
- php-xml
- python >= 2.x
- Emboss (seqret and transeq)
- MySQLdb for python

====================
Install
====================

First, create an empty database in mysql, then you have two options:
 o Guided install: sh install.sh
 o Manual install:
	sh config_site.sh <base site url>
	sh config_fs.sh <site location in apache dir>
	sh config_db.sh <database> <database user> <database password>
	cd db && sh import.sh <database> <user> <password
	cd scripts && sh run_all.sh
  # update user set password = 'admin_password' where name = 'admin'

You should also install the following cron jobs:
0 0 * * * /usr/bin/python $(PWD)/scripts/gc_subsequences.py

To install the NCBI taxonomy database, you should do:
  cd scripts && sh ncbi.sh

To use some EMBOSS tools you need to create the PRINTS database:
  # sudo sh generate_prints.sh

To use some EMBOSS tools you need to create the PROSITE database:
  # sudo sh generate_prosite.sh

To install extra labels please run one of the following scripts:

  # python script.py <database password>

label_antigenic.py      label_letters.py        label_sigcleave.py
label_chips.py          label_epestfind.py      label_patmatmotifs.py
label_iep.py            label_pscan.py
